請試述此二項方案之內容，並比較兩者內容的差異性。（20 分）', '[]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:36+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "16918ff39647", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113100", "c": "108", "s": "0805", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "甲、申論題部分", "subject": "環境與職業衛生", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、113年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": "二", "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "publichealth", "db_exam_id": "public-health-specialist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
